        {
            "title": "【大學融資】港大10億美元債：為建北都另覓財路？拆解集資利弊！",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uc9ACeA_3p4twmJw3uCIHg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/d77e2ada8e8a909294b2c28b07a9c013\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
